column3: It was really nice to stay in casa caracol! Seems like this house is really famous among tourists so while I stay there I saw a lot of people taking photos in front of the house. And the house owner Raquel is so kind, she gave us some fish that she just bought in a market as a present. And Michelle kept asking me if I am doing well or not, and she responds really fast !
